tion with vector bosons and scalars at the LHC. If the\nparameter space of the model that favors $H^\\pm \\to W^\\pm \\gamma$ is realized\nin Nature, we estimate that there could be a considerable amount of such events\nin the present LHC data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Nov 2013 13:22:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 7 Dec 2013 08:19:47 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 5 Dec 2014 15:14:01 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 9 Apr 2015 15:01:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-08"}
