al days in which the brightness increased by\n~15-20% in one object, as well a smaller flare in another. Two AGN showed only\nsmall, ~1-2%, fluctuations in brightness.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 17 Nov 2013 19:28:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 19 Mar 2014 01:28:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-01-27"}
