ginating from an actual travel blog text corpus. To\nverify the quality of the result, we generate grid-based maps visualizing the\nspatial extent of the various relations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Nov 2013 09:06:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-11-21"}
